'''Shyaka Kagamé''' (yavutse 1983), ni umunya[[Rwanda]] uba muri [[Ubusuwisi|Swiss]] . Azwi cyane nk'umuyobozi wa firime ''Bounty'' ishimwa cyane<ref>https://www.jeuneafrique.com/auteurs/s-kagame/</ref><ref>https://www.swissfilms.ch/en/film_search/filmdetails/-/id_person/A0D95F5AFCF14B5C8EF46AEF5928AB9F</ref>.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse mu 1983 i Geneve mu [[Busuwisi]] ku babyeyi b'u [[Rwanda]].<ref>https://www.swissfilms.ch/fr/film_search/filmdetails/-/id_person/A0D95F5AFCF14B5C8EF46AEF5928AB9F</ref> 

== Umwuga ==
Mbere yo kwinjira muri sinema, yize siyanse ya politiki. Mu 2009, Kagamé yatangiye umwuga we wa filime nk'umuyobozi wungirije hamwe n’umukinnyi wa firime wa Geneve Frédéric Baillif<ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm4433963/</ref>.  Muri Kamena 2017, Kagamé yerekanye bwa mbere ''Bounty''<ref>https://letterboxd.com/director/shyaka-kagame/</ref> .  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yerekanwa mu birori byinshi bya firime. Inyandiko irihariye kubera nta majwi arenga, kubazwa cyangwa isura ya kamera. Filime ivuga kubibazo bijyanye numwirondoro wabirabura  babasuwisi.<ref>http://www.film-documentaire.fr/4DACTION/w_fiche_film/51190_1</ref><ref>https://www.toulouse.fr/documents/106827/10951271/Biographie_Shyaka_Kagame/35aad3c0-2855-46e3-930a-4b9e1dad8332</ref> 

